{"tid":1728430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民口罩","createTime":"2019-11-17T01:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T01:55:51.000Z","uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1fe9752d0693665b10b8523d8df820767766987e","tid":1728430,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:11:12.000Z","msg":"到底係唔係已經冇人戴？<br />\n我出街行到邊都唔見人戴口罩,得我一個戴,行過個個都望一望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12ab6e7e2c46a02ae20f738333c00ec4b1a633f","tid":1728430,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:11:54.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=c76f6d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=897bb8fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"0e1b3a228a8005e50a6f16e4c443693adce5413e","tid":1728430,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:12:18.000Z","msg":"繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有權戴口罩"},{"pid":"3b4e75786933540d460cb4b51e489cbd092607a7","tid":1728430,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:12:48.000Z","msg":"係唔係見無人戴所以唔敢戴？"},{"pid":"61b1debbc075177facbb4ecbb6b992dbff04989b","tid":1728430,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:14:32.000Z","msg":"唔係取消左既話 請繼續全民口罩日"},{"pid":"a6804bb27255e97e6c4c7355841bddbf1d1b1ce5","tid":1728430,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:16:38.000Z","msg":"我有權"},{"pid":"f30184a8b01043a3073cc62c925a1d5ea2d5b06f","tid":1728430,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:16:48.000Z","msg":"帶口罩"},{"pid":"f7422aa4c0ce164d5397c19e955cf6712b7e9142","tid":1728430,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:26:27.000Z","msg":"有！ 我都見唔到隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家快啲歸隊"},{"pid":"95f9b4a53e376aed5bea4215d4ded88947abb1f7","tid":1728430,"uid":69629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:29:35.000Z","msg":"真係無咩人戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31588e682d98d1e1bc59d99cf1d0d4b6f280e0b4","tid":1728430,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"二噁英就